            "notes": "This deck focuses on utilizing Slimefoot and Squee as the commanders for an aggressive playstyle in Duel Commander. The deck includes a mix of creatures, removal spells, and ramp cards to apply consistent pressure on the opponent. By combining cards like Goblin Bombardment for direct damage, Skullclamp for card advantage, and Birthing Pod for creature tutoring, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent with a swarm of creatures while generating additional value from sacrificing creatures. The mana base is designed to support the aggressive strategy by ensuring consistent access to all necessary colors of mana. Overall, the deck aims to quickly establish board presence, disrupt the opponent's game plan, and close out the game efficiently."
